<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<railml xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:sehwa="http://www.sehwa.co.kr/railml" version="2.5" xmlns="http://www.railml.org/schemas/2013">
  <infrastructure id="inf001" name="Default Infrastructure">
    <tracks>
      <track id="tr1" mainDir="down" code="plain">
        <trackTopology>
          <trackBegin pos="0" id="tb1" />
          <trackEnd pos="20" id="te1">
            <connection id="ce1" ref="cb2" />
          </trackEnd>
        </trackTopology>
      </track>
      <track id="tr2" mainDir="down" code="plain">
        <trackTopology>
          <trackBegin pos="0" id="tb2">
            <connection id="cb2" ref="ce1" />
          </trackBegin>
          <trackEnd pos="30" id="te2" />
          <connections>
            <switch id="sw1" pos="0" trackContinueCourse="straight" normalPosition="straight">
              <additionalName name="sw1" />
              <connection id="c1-cb3" ref="cb3" orientation="outgoing" course="left" />
            </switch>
          </connections>
        </trackTopology>
      </track>
      <track id="tr3" mainDir="down" code="corner">
        <trackTopology>
          <trackBegin pos="0" id="tb3">
            <connection id="cb3" ref="c1-cb3" />
          </trackBegin>
          <trackEnd pos="54" id="te3" />
        </trackTopology>
      </track>
    </tracks>
  </infrastructure>
  <infrastructureVisualizations>
    <visualization id="vis1" infrastructureRef="inf001">
      <lineVis>
        <trackVis ref="tr1">
          <trackElementVis ref="tb1">
            <position x="80" y="120" />
          </trackElementVis>
          <trackElementVis ref="te1">
            <position x="100" y="120" />
          </trackElementVis>
        </trackVis>
        <trackVis ref="tr2">
          <trackElementVis ref="tb2">
            <position x="100" y="120" />
          </trackElementVis>
          <trackElementVis ref="te2">
            <position x="130" y="120" />
          </trackElementVis>
        </trackVis>
        <trackVis ref="tr3">
          <trackElementVis ref="tb3">
            <position x="100" y="120" />
          </trackElementVis>
          <trackElementVis ref="te3">
            <position x="130" y="80" />
          </trackElementVis>
          <trackElementVis ref="tr3_mid">
            <position x="120" y="80" />
          </trackElementVis>
        </trackVis>
      </lineVis>
      <objectVis ref="sw1">
        <position x="100" y="120" />
      </objectVis>
    </visualization>
  </infrastructureVisualizations>
</railml>
